## 8. Troubleshooting

| Problem | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Highlight does not appear on an element | Verify the `id` attribute was added to the JSX element and the `selector` in the step matches exactly (e.g. `#tour-network-search`) |
| Tour does not navigate to the next page | Confirm `nextRoute` is set on the correct step, and the route string matches the actual Next.js path exactly |
| TourCard does not appear | Confirm `cardComponent={TourCard}` is passed to `<NextStep>` in `layout.tsx` |
| `useNextStep must be used within NextStepProvider` error | Ensure `NextStepProvider` is in `app/layout.tsx` above any component using `useNextStep()` |
| Highlight mis-positioned in scrollable container | Wrap the scrollable container with `<NextStepViewport>...</NextStepViewport>` |
| Animation not working | Run `npm list motion` â€” reinstall with `npm install motion` if missing |
| TypeScript error on `Tour` type | Use `import type { Tour } from 'nextstepjs';` |

